AEIS (Aegis Endpoint Integrity Systems) is developed under the ARCHE framework 
to provide endpoint-first defense and sovereignty in digital life. 
Our focus is on integrity, transparency, and user-controlled security.

AEIS equips individuals to:
• Secure their digital identity
• Preserve the integrity of logs and system activity
• Maintain full ownership of their security posture

Empowering ordinary users with enterprise-class security principles.
